{"tid":625083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"38歲田中麗奈為「盛情款待」現身台北 現場大秀中文","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T09:26:15.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47a8d329632a63f55cc13761a8f11f474e714524","tid":625083,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"台日合拍新片「盛情款待」今晚在台北舉行盛大首映，導演陳鈺杰率領主要演員王柏傑、楊烈、呂雪鳳、姚淳耀一同出席。片中有吃重表現的日本女星田中麗奈也專程趕來現場，與台北觀眾見面。學習中文已小有成績的她，不但在電影裡能夠用中文說台詞，在首映現場也特地以中文向粉絲打招呼，表現相當真誠可愛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/144807_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F144807_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=950660b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/144838_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F144838_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=84e7dd05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/11/144908_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F11%2F144908_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=67fbfe6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7ef1fc02991ef82e65ef07280269f3977c4a811","tid":625083,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:52:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b4ac81b50d1ebce585f8937d0fc7301e1eb160e","tid":625083,"uid":14497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:55:12.000Z","msg":"以前好中田中麗奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc433766b0932fd47124a77432b00a0c79803aba","tid":625083,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:41:37.000Z","msg":"初中個陣有個FD好鍾意佢